Sentencas: The creep damageability and long-term strength of a tubular solid oxide fuel cell are studied.
Titulo: A Study of the Creep Damageability of Tubular Solid Oxide Fuel Cell

Sentencas: The method for the solution of the initial boundary value problem of creep and damageability is based on the joint application of the R-function and the Runge-Kutta-Merson methods.
Titulo: A Study of the Creep Damageability of Tubular Solid Oxide Fuel Cell

Sentencas: An example of the calculation of the creep and long-term strength of a Siemens-Westinghouse fuel cell is given.
Titulo: A Study of the Creep Damageability of Tubular Solid Oxide Fuel Cell
